definitions.text:
@làm cỏ
* verb
- to weed, to shoot up

@làm chủ
* verb
- to own, to hold the ownesship

@làm cho
* verb
- to cause, to make

@làm cỗ
- Prepare a feast (on a death anniversary, wedding...)
=Làm cỗ sẵn+To beat the bush for another to catch the birds

@làm chiêm
- Make preparations for the fifth-month rice crop
=Gặt mùa xong là phải lo làm chiêm+To have to see to the preparations for the fifth-month rice crop immediately after the harvest of the autumn crop (the tenth-month rice)
